name: Teeny Flower Zipper Pouch
description:
This pouch is made using a sweet flower print fabric on the exterior, and aqua chevron print on the interior. These pouches are wonderful for organizing your purse, keeping cosmetics together, or using as a small clutch. Or, give as a gift for teacher, friend, family member, or yourself. So many possibilities! 
Fully lined and interfaced to hold shape. The bottom is boxed to stand upright.

Measures: 7" tall, 9" wide, with a 3.5" flat bottom.

Care Instructions: Hand wash in cold water and lay flat to dry.

Made in my smoke free home studio

name: Merry Hoot
description:
For the lover of all things Christmas, the Merry Hoot is a perfect gift or decoration.  These adorable little owls make great companions for babies, kids and adults alike. They are bright, colorful, cuddly and sure to bring a smile to your face. The Merry Hoot is made using a a classic Christmas fabric along with coordinating red stripe, and green dot.

Made using 100% cotton fabric, eco friendly felt, and hypo allergenic fiber filling. The eyes are hand embroidered on, so there are no small pieces to worry about for the little ones. Measures 17.5" tall.

**This item is Made to Order. Please check current turn around times. Placement of fabric may vary, but same fabric will be used. **

name: Cluster Necklace
description:
This pretty necklace is a fantastic gift for a friend, teacher or yourself. It's just pretty and would add a little pop of color and happy to your everyday wardrobe. Made using three different sized/shapped czech glass beads, and antiqued bronze chian and a lobster clasp closure.  

The following lengths are available: 18" or 20".

name: Camera Necklace
description:
Are you a lover of photography or, know someone who is? Here's the perfect gift for that special someone.  This necklace can be worn dressed up or down. The pretty antiqued bronze charm is paired with czech glass beads for a pop of color.  Features a lobster clasp closure. Can also be made in two different chain lengths. 

If the bead colors don't strike your fancy I can make one with a pairing more suited to your taste. Just contact me via the Contact Page. 

Grab yours while you can!

name: Customize your own Hootie Hoot
description:
Who can resist a Hootie Hoot? These adorable little owls make the perfect companions for babies, kids and adults alike.  They are bright, colorful, cuddly and sure to bring a smile to your face. This listing is for the "Customize your own Hootie Hoot." Together we can come up with the perfect fabric pairings to make your one of a kind owl. Once payment is made please contact me via the Contact page.  I will need to know what colors you would like to incorporate into your owl.  I will then email you with several fabric choices. Once you choose your fabrics I will then begin to work on your owl. 

Made using 100% cotton fabric, eco friendly felt, and hypo allergenic fiber filling. The eyes are hand embroidered on, so there are no small pieces to worry about for the little ones.  Measures 17.5" tall.

This is a Made to Order item. Please check current turn around times (they are subject to change).  Due to the nature of the item payment is expected before any work can begin. Thank you for your understanding.
